description: King Kone is an ice cream parlor on wheels! We are a family owned business based in Los Angeles, and serve all of L.A. County as well as surrounding areas.In a city that keeps us all so busy and at a loss for extra time, convenience is bliss. King Kone will come to you for any occasion! Our quality and creative treats will leave a smile on your face, and your family and friends will love it.
name: King Kone
